### =============================================================================
### FILE: admin-authz.http
### PURPOSE (EN):
### - Manual admin authorization API scenario for quick verification.
### - Includes resource creation, role-resource assignment, and listing resources.
### - Requires a valid ADMIN JWT.
### MUC DICH:
### - Kich ban goi API quan tri phan quyen de test nhanh bang tay.
### - Bao gom tao resource, gan role-resource va kiem tra danh sach resource.
### - Dung kem JWT cua tai khoan ADMIN.
### =============================================================================

@host = http://localhost:8080
@adminToken = REPLACE_WITH_ADMIN_JWT

### 1) Tao resource GET /api/students/**
POST {{host}}/api/admin/authz/resources
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resourceCode": "STUDENT_API_READ",
  "resourceGroup": "STUDENT",
  "actionCode": "READ",
  "name": "Read student API",
  "urlPattern": "/api/students/**",
  "httpMethod": "GET"
}

###
### 2) Tao resource POST /api/students
POST {{host}}/api/admin/authz/resources
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resourceCode": "STUDENT_API_CREATE",
  "resourceGroup": "STUDENT",
  "actionCode": "CREATE",
  "name": "Create student API",
  "urlPattern": "/api/students",
  "httpMethod": "POST"
}

###
### 3) Gan role USER duoc doc student
POST {{host}}/api/admin/authz/roles/USER/resources/STUDENT_API_READ
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###
### 4) Gan role ADMIN duoc tao student
POST {{host}}/api/admin/authz/roles/ADMIN/resources/STUDENT_API_CREATE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###
### 5) Xem danh sach resource hien co
GET {{host}}/api/admin/authz/resources
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###
### 6) Go gan role-resource
DELETE {{host}}/api/admin/authz/roles/USER/resources/STUDENT_API_READ
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
